data.description: Nestled in the desirable Southside of Corpus Christi, this home epitomizes charm and comfort. With a fully bricked exterior and vaulted ceilings inside, it boasts a welcoming ambiance. The interior features fresh paint, tile, and laminate flooring, ensuring both style and easy maintenance. The open-plan layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, ideal for hosting gatherings. The kitchen is complete with ample storage and countertop space. The primary bedroom has decorative ceilings and a walk-in closet. Outside, a large yard with a covered patio awaits, complete with ceiling fans and provisions for outdoor entertainment like TV viewing and barbecuing. The convenient Southside location offers easy access to amenities, schools, parks, and more, enhancing the quality of daily living. This Southside gem is a haven of modern living and convenience, blending indoor comfort with outdoor relaxation. Enjoy the conveniences of Southside living and schedule a showing today!
